---
import ShareableQuote from "../../ShareableQuote.astro";
---

<section
    id="tiempo-profundo"
    class="wheat-relative wheat-font-serif wheat-min-h-screen wheat-flex wheat-items-center wheat-justify-center wheat-py-12 wheat-py-24@md wheat-overflow-hidden wheat-deeptime"
>
    <div
        class="wheat-absolute wheat-inset-0 wheat-flex wheat-items-center wheat-deeptime-landscape"
        id="landscape-mover"
    >
        <div class="wheat-deeptime-track wheat-flex wheat-items-center">
            <div class="wheat-deeptime-circle wheat-deeptime-circle--1"></div>
            <div class="wheat-deeptime-circle wheat-deeptime-circle--2"></div>
            <div class="wheat-deeptime-circle wheat-deeptime-circle--3"></div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="wheat-w-full wheat-relative" id="section1-container">
        <div class="wheat-w-full wheat-flex wheat-flex-col wheat-justify-center">
            <div class="wheat-relative wheat-deeptime-content wheat-max-w-4xl wheat-mx-auto wheat-px-6 wheat-text-center">
                <span class="trigo-chapter wheat-deeptime-chapter wheat-text-xs wheat-text-sm@md wheat-tracking-widest wheat-uppercase wheat-block wheat-mb-4">
                    El Tiempo Profundo
                </span>
                <h2 class="wheat-text-4xl wheat-text-6xl@md wheat-font-bold wheat-mb-8 wheat-deeptime-title">
                    200.000 Años de Silencio
                </h2>

                <div class="wheat-space-y-6 wheat-space-y-8@md wheat-deeptime-card wheat-p-6 wheat-p-8@md wheat-rounded-lg wheat-mx-auto">
                    <p class="wheat-text-xl wheat-text-2xl@md wheat-leading-relaxed wheat-deeptime-text-primary">
                        Durante el 99% de nuestra historia, fuimos nómadas. El mundo no nos
                        pertenecía; nosotros pertenecíamos al mundo.
                    </p>
                    <p class="wheat-text-base wheat-text-lg@md wheat-deeptime-text-secondary">
                        Cazábamos, recolectábamos, y seguíamos adelante. La vida era peligrosa, sí,
                        pero era ligera. <ShareableQuote
                            quote="No teníamos dueños, ni muros, ni dioses enfadados."
                        />
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .wheat-deeptime {
        color: #e7e5e4;
    }
    .wheat-deeptime-landscape {
        transition: transform 100ms ease-linear;
    }
    .wheat-deeptime-track {
        width: 300vw;
        height: 100%;
        background: linear-gradient(to right, #1c1917, #292524, #0c0a09);
        justify-content: space-around;
        opacity: 0.5;
    }
    .wheat-deeptime-circle {
        border-radius: 50%;
        filter: blur(64px);
        opacity: 0.3;
        width: 16rem;
        height: 16rem;
    }
    @media (min-width: 768px) {
        .wheat-deeptime-circle {
            width: 24rem;
            height: 24rem;
        }
        .wheat-space-y-8\@md > * + * {
            margin-top: 2rem;
        }
        .wheat-p-8\@md {
            padding: 2rem;
        }
    }
    .wheat-deeptime-circle--1 {
        background-color: #44403c;
    }
    .wheat-deeptime-circle--2 {
        background-color: #57534e;
    }
    .wheat-deeptime-circle--3 {
        background-color: #292524;
    }
    .wheat-deeptime-content {
        z-index: 10;
    }
    .wheat-deeptime-chapter {
        color: rgba(217, 119, 6, 0.6);
    }
    .wheat-deeptime-title {
        color: #e7e5e4;
    }
    .wheat-deeptime-card {
        backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
        background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        border: 1px solid rgba(120, 113, 108, 0.5);
        max-width: 42rem;
    }
    .wheat-deeptime-text-primary {
        color: #d6d3d1;
    }
    .wheat-deeptime-text-secondary {
        color: #a8a29e;
    }
</style>
